		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This diaphanous cloth seems made of shadows and twinkling stars. With it you can vanish from sight.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Head Slot</b><b>:</b> Rare</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>Gain a +4 item bonus to Stealth checks.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Move Action)</b></p><p>You and an adjacent ally become invisible until either of you leaves the squares you occupy or until the end of the encounter.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Immediate Interrupt)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> An enemy attacks you or an ally adjacent to you.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> The target of the triggering attack becomes invisible until the end of your next turn.</p>",
